title: Dragonball Z - Yo The Return of Son-Goku and Friends
description: Two years have passed since the battle with Majin Boo. Mr.Satan&#039;s hotel, built as a commemoration of the victory over Boo, is finally complete!!Goku and the other fighters are invited as guests. While Goku and the others are enjoying the party, a strange pod falls to Earth. Inside, a sharp-eyed Saiyan detects strong fighting abilities and takes a small alien along to the party! When the Saiyan encounters Vegeta, his words shock everyone!!
